Specification

When turning on no sound is played
Press a button and there will be a pause of 60 seconds (should be configurable) before the ring tone plays
When the ring tone is playing, pressing a button will make it stop, if the button is not pressed to stop it should play for 30 seconds (should be configurable)
Pressing the button again will go through the same steps above
Volume setting should be persistent between being powered off and on
